org.digijava.module.aim.annotations.interchange

Annotation Type Independent


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=FIELD)
public @interface Independent
    Used to mark the boundary of the object tree which is owned by the root object. For example agreements are mapped via Interchangeable as is they are part of the activity when they are not. This information is used initialize object correctly during deserialization. If a value is specified in json then it will be replaced with a fresh new object. Otherwise existing object reference is kept as is. Works only for fields where type is object.
